flowchart LR
    User[User at interactive Windows session]
    Rules[Untrusted declarative rule packs]
    Disk[Untrusted local filesystem and metadata]

    subgraph Standard[Standard-user integrity boundary]
        App[CLYR WinUI app]
        CLI[CLYR CLI]
        Core[Core services and protected-resource policy]
        Plan[Immutable ten-minute cleanup plan and dry run]
        Confirm[Digest-bound explicit confirmation]
        Journal[(Product-owned journal and receipts)]
        Pipe[Unique first-instance local named-pipe server]
        RuleValidator[Strict schema and rule validator]

        App --> Core
        CLI --> Core
        RuleValidator --> Core
        Core --> Plan
        Plan --> Confirm
        Confirm --> Journal
        Journal --> Pipe
    end

    Rules --> RuleValidator
    Disk -->|Read-only metadata in early phases| Core
    User --> App
    User --> CLI

    UAC{Windows UAC consent after CLYR confirmation}
    Pipe --> UAC

    subgraph Elevated[High-integrity boundary - future Phase 6 only]
        Helper[Short-lived CLYR elevated helper]
        Revalidate[Authenticate peers and revalidate complete typed batch]
        Registry[Compiled capability and adapter registry]
        Executor[Minimum approved action executor]

        Helper --> Revalidate
        Registry --> Revalidate
        Revalidate --> Executor
    end

    UAC -->|Denied: zero mutation| Journal
    UAC -->|Approved: launch exact signed helper| Helper
    Pipe <-->|One authenticated versioned request and receipt| Helper
    Executor -->|Exact supported operation| WindowsAPI[Approved Windows or vendor mechanism]
    WindowsAPI -->|Bounded result| Helper
    Helper -->|Completed, PartiallyCompleted, or Failed receipt| Journal

    Protected[Protected resource, changed target, stale plan, or Prohibited risk]
    Rejected[Reject before mutation; no user or admin override]
    Protected --> Rejected
    Revalidate -->|Any item invalid| Rejected

    Arbitrary[Arbitrary command, executable, wildcard, or generic path request]
    Arbitrary --> Rejected
    Rules -.->|Cannot cross directly| Helper

    Phase0[Phase 0 status: documentation only; no cleanup or elevation exists]
    Phase0 -.-> Plan

